Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 馬車?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會停在這
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳{\fnDFMaruGothic-Bd}~{\fn華康中圓體}們{\fnDFMaruGothic-Bd}~{\fn華康中圓體}回{\fnDFMaruGothic-Bd}~{\fn華康中圓體}來{\fnDFMaruGothic-Bd}~{\fn華康中圓體}啦{\fnDFMaruGothic-Bd}~!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真學不會呢 蕾菲亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實她期待很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:24.48,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,真柔軟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 艾絲小姐!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:29.78,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,不要光道歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 蕾菲亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人欲罷不能啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我!!
